data.description: Looking for that Florida house that combines size, style, and location with a newer build? Look no further than 4432 Collingswood Blvd., Port Charlotte! This 2019 built, 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 3 car garage measures in at 2438 square feet & combines the size you're looking for with convenient locale. Inside you'll find a spacious open concept floorplan featuring a modern coastal grey motif that continues throughout the house. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and overlooks the main living area. Great restaurants, shopping, Charlotte Harbor, & the world famous Tamiami Trail are all only a short 5 minute drive away. Call today for more information and to set up your private showing!
